arStrings.szText:
{c_label}Experience: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} Needed to increase your hero's Level.
{icon:bullet} Gained by killing monsters and completing quests.

{c_label}Dodge Chance: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} The chance to dodge incoming attacks.
{icon:bullet} Dodged attacks do no damage.

{c_label}Armor: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} Reduces Physical damage taken from enemies of equal Level by {c_number}{s2}{/c_number}.
{icon:bullet} {c_number}9,230{/c} Armor is required for maximum reduction against Level {c_number}100{/c} enemies and beyond.

{c_label}Hitpoints: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} The amount of Life you have.
{icon:bullet} Hitpoints are based on your character Level and the armor you are wearing.

{c_label}Attack Power: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} An evaluation of the damage you deal.
{icon:bullet} Based on your offensive stats scaled with your currently wielded weapon's damage and speed.

{c_label}Maximum Life: {c_number}{s1}{/c_number}{/c}
{icon:bullet} If you lose all your Life, you die.
{icon:bullet} The total of the Base Life for your Level and any additional bonuses.
